<h1>
Smart Infinity Glove with Heuristic Technology
</h1>
<h2>
Introduction
</h2>
<p>
A smart wearable that is made using smart technologies that blend together in a compact glove. Some notable features include
</p>
<ul>
<li>Gesture recognition</li>
<li>Position estimation of fingers</li>
<li>Pulse sensor</li>
</ul>
